high_descs: Move right to face the table next to the bed.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Put the knife on the plate on the table.
Pick up the plate with the knife from the table.
Turn right to exit the room, turn right to walk the passage to enter the bathroom on the left to reach the sink.
Put the plate with the knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with the knife in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and there is a table near the bed.
Take the knife from the table.
Put it on the plate which is white colored.
Take the plate with knife from the table.
And then go to the wash room.
Put the plate with knife into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Placed the plate with knife into the wash room sink.

high_descs: Turn right and move to an armchair with a table beside it.
Take a knife from the table.
Stick the knife into a plate on the table.
Pick up the plate with the knife from the table.
Turn right, leave the room, take a step right then immediately enter a restroom on the left, where you walk up to a sink.
Put the plate with the knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Get the plate and knife in the restroom's sink
